StatementHelp.#cdata:
Syntax: PIE chart-variable(s) </ option(s)>; 

Creates a pie chart in which the size of a pie slice represents the value of the chart statistic 
for that category of data in relation to the total chart statistic for all categories.

Syntax: PIE3D chart-variable(s) </ option(s)>; 

Creates a 3D pie chart in which the size of a pie slice represents the value of the chart statistic
for that category of data in relation to the total chart statistic for all categories.
